"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        Cancel response payloads with different cancellation results.
        """
a = payloads.CancelResponsePayload(cancellation_result=enums.
    CancellationResult.FAILED)
b = payloads.CancelResponsePayload(cancellation_result=enums.
    CancellationResult.COMPLETED)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
